headline.print_headline: Chinese Woman Scales Everest From Nepal Side
headline.main: Chinese Woman Scales Everest From Nepal Side

docs.snippet: A Chinese woman and five Sherpa guides have scaled Mount Everest, becoming the first team to reach the peak from the Nepal side since a deadly avalanche last month sent climbers home, officials said Saturday....
docs.lead_paragraph: A Chinese woman and five Sherpa guides have scaled Mount Everest, becoming the first team to reach the peak from the Nepal side since a deadly avalanche last month sent climbers home, officials said Saturday.
